headline: Darden Restaurants Stock: Is DRI Outperforming the Consumer Discretionary Sector?
summary: While Darden Restaurants has outpaced the broader consumer discretionary sector over the past year, analysts maintain a measured outlook on its future performance, balancing recent gains with a watchful eye on potential headwinds.
